            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B6%B4%E7%9D%80%E7%9D%A1%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B6%B4%E7%9D%80%E7%9D%A1%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#趴着睡危害脊柱#</span></a>】睡醒感觉腰酸背疼，可能是睡姿不对导致的。① <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%96%E5%85%AB%E7%9D%A1%E5%A7%BF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%85%B0%E9%85%B8%E8%83%8C%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%96%E5%85%AB%E7%9D%A1%E5%A7%BF%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%85%B0%E9%85%B8%E8%83%8C%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#外八睡姿可能导致腰酸背痛#</span></a>；②过度蜷缩睡；③趴着睡；④歪着头睡。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4985672725889047" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1gy1hlfat93dndj21hc0u0420.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UpKBxveJlx08bqsUSjwc01041200udFa0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1704474868&amp;ssig=UHU7Q18ipw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/aTqkCdWylx08bqsTOfmg01041200eyu80E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1704474868&amp;ssig=RqIJwICauK&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ed1W0WAXlx08bqsTwxIY0104120091Gc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cx9YB1mmR49jS&amp;Expires=1704474868&amp;ssig=1AHzCa46%2FP&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4985672725889047" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
